## SMTP config for bug report email relay (server-side).
## Copy to `.env` on the server and fill in values.
## Never commit `.env` (it's in .gitignore).
#
## Required:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com
# SMTP_USER=your-smtp-user
# SMTP_PASS=your-smtp-password
#
## Optional:
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_SSL=false
#
## Bug report mail routing:
# BUGREPORT_TO=admin@schellenberger.biz
# BUGREPORT_FROM=admin@schellenberger.biz

